title: Why AMD Stock Surged Last Week
description: Shares of Advanced Micro Devices (NASDAQ: AMD) climbed 14% this past week, according to data from S&P Global Market Intelligence.  AMD's shareholders breathed sighs of relief when the chipmaker released its fourth-quarter earnings report after the market close on Tuesday.  Going into the week, investors were fearful that AMD's results could mimic those of Intel (NASDAQ: INTC).
